I'm stumped at the moment, but still thinking about it.  Probably best to make a list of the actual, and preceived, issues with the warrior class, and see if there's any game balance neutral changes that can address them adequately.  <br>
<br>
My personal desire would be to see that a warriors &quot;natural&quot; strength (tanking) be enhanced without nerfing other classes (monk/rog DPS + aggro reduction, monk HP + damage avoidance, hybrid taunt spells, etc.) or seriously imbalancing the game/existing encounters...<br>
<br>
Gonna be a trick, and I'm pretty sure extra warrior DPS isn't the answer.  Don't know what will be tho, hope Verant doesn't botch it. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
